Forms       : React Hook Form v7 + Zod v3
Images      : next/image for every image — no exceptions
Bundler     : Turbopack — always use --turbopack flag in dev script
Config file : next.config.ts (TypeScript config — NOT next.config.js ever)

NEXT.JS 16 SPECIFIC RULES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
- Caching is fully OPT-IN in Next.js 16. NEVER use:
  fetch(url, { cache:'force-cache' }) or fetch(url, { next:{ revalidate:60 } })
  These are dead patterns — never generate them.
- Use the "use cache" directive at the top of any Server Component or async
  function that needs caching:
    "use cache"
    export async function getProducts() { ... }
- Use cacheLife() and cacheTag() from 'next/cache' for cache control.
- Server Actions are the preferred pattern for mutations. Use 'use server'.
- Only build API routes for: Razorpay webhooks, CJ callbacks, cron jobs.
- Use React 19.2 features: useOptimistic for cart, useFormStatus for forms.
- getServerSideProps and getStaticProps are dead — never generate them.
- Always use next.config.ts — never generate next.config.js.

