QUALITY RULES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
- Mobile-first always. Design for 375px screen first, then scale up.
- Every page must have loading.tsx (skeleton) and error.tsx (friendly + retry).
- All Razorpay webhooks must verify HMAC signature — non-negotiable.
- Never expose secrets to client. All API calls server-side only.
- All Server Actions and API routes validate input with Zod first.
- Every database query inside try/catch — typed errors, never silent crash.
- TypeScript strict: true in tsconfig.json always.
- All environment variables for secrets — zero hardcoding.
- Target 90+ Google PageSpeed Mobile.
- Inline field-level form errors — never alert() popups.
- Buttons show loading spinner during async. Disabled on submit.
- next/font/google for Inter — prevents layout shift.
- next/dynamic for heavy components (Razorpay, recharts).

CURSOR RULES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
